<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Pfalz-Neumarkt</head><p>Der Rat gewährt auf Bitten des Adressaten dem Juden Strölein N. trotz vergangener Untaten und Bestrafung, sich in den kommenden zwei Jahren Nürnberg bis auf zwei Meilen anzunähern.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_584" id="291r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_584_r2l21">Hercʒog <expan>Johannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> von Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_584_r2l22"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> vns haben <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnde dıe nehſt bey <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_584_r2l23">weſen ſeyn wol geſagt / wıe eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade mıt Jn auch ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_584_r2l24">redt vnd aber begert hab als von ſtrölein Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc . Nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_584_r2l25">haben wır <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> reͣten vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vormals <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_584_r2l26">wır <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſtrölein Jud gepüſʒt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> von ſweͣrs merklıchs ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_584_r2l27">handelns <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ er bey vns getan . vnd da mit er gröſſer </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_585" id="291v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l1">ſtraff wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchuldt</expan> hett / <expan>Dıeſ<ex>elbe</ex></expan> puſſ ʒu halten er iren Jüdıſchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l2">eyde öffenlıch geſworn hat / Vnd ob keinrley bett für Jn beſcheͣhe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l3">daʒ Jn das daran niht <expan>fürtrage<ex>n</ex></expan> ſol . / daʒ vns niht füklıch ıſt . <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l4">Juden <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> . in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtatt ein oder awſʒ <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu laſſen / Seıd <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l5">eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> meynt / daʒ Jr <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Juden ʒu <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> notdurft ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l6">wol bedurffet / So ſecʒen wir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>nthalben</expan> / auf <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Juden / daʒ er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l7">dıe <expan>nehſtkünſtıg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒwey Jare . ʒwo meyl wegs von <expan>vnſer<ex>r</ex></expan> ſtat hin dan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l8"><expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mag / daʒ wir <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu eren <expan>dıeſ<ex>elbe</ex></expan> ʒeıt <expan>dawıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l9">nıht ſein wellen / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd wolgefallen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207349990_3890">etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> . <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> iij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> dorothee <expan>vırg<ex>in</ex>ıs</expan> </ab>
<note place="bottomcentral">
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l12">darnach <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> <expan>kathedr<ex>am</ex></expan> ſein für Rat <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> hans vom <expan>Eglofſſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> <expan>Ritt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l13">Vnd ludwıcg / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> hercʒog <expan>Johanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> . mit <expan>eıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>glaubbr<ex>ief</ex></expan> / Vnd die von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_r1l14">deʒ <expan>ÿcʒg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex></expan> . <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / dem Juden mer Jar ʒu <expan>erlaube<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207368810_3910">etlıch 
<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del> meyl neher </ab>
</note>
<note place="marginleft">
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207430850_3974"><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> Jn iſt ʒu geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207433156_3979">der Rat meint </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207435703_3984">beÿ den <expan>obgeſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>Jar<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207438450_3989">ʒubeleıben <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207441747_3994">ein meÿl wegs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207444976_3999">mag er neher </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207448210_4004">herʒu <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207451251_4009"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>ere<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207456457_4014">als man ſagt das <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207459504_4019">auf den <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_585_line_1592207464548_4024"><expan>obgeſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> maſſ </ab></note>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_584" id="291r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Johanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns haben <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        frewnde, die nehst bey <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> gewesen seyn, wol gesagt, wie ewr
                                <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade mit in auch geredt und
                        aber begert hab als von Strölein juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. Nu
                        haben wir <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> reͣten und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        vormals <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, daz wir
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> Strölein jud gepüszt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> von sweͣrs merklichs verhandelns
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz er bey uns getan und damit er
                        grösser <pb facs="#facs_585" id="291v"/>straff wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schuldt</expan>
                        hett, <expan>dies<ex>elbe</ex></expan> puss zu halten er iren jüdischen eyde
                        öffenlich gesworn hat, und, ob keinrley bett für in bescheͣhe, daz in das
                        daran niht <expan>fürtrage<ex>n</ex></expan> sol, daz uns niht füklich ist,
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> juden
                            <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> statt
                        ein oder awsz <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu lassen. Seid
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> meynt, daz ir
                                <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> juden zu
                            <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> notdurft so wol bedurffet, so seczen wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>nthalben</expan> auf
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> juden, daz er die
                                <expan>nehstkünstig<ex>en</ex></expan> zwey jare zwo meyl wegs von
                                <expan>unser<ex>r</ex></expan> stat hin dan
                            <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mag, daz wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu eren <expan>dies<ex>elbe</ex></expan> zeit
                                <expan>dawid<ex>er</ex></expan> niht sein wellen. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Dorothee <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan>. <app>
<note place="bottom"> Darnach <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan>
<expan>kathedr<ex>am</ex></expan></q>23.02.1423</note>
</app> sein für rat <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> Hans vom
                                    <expan>Eglofsst<ex>ein</ex></expan>,
                                    <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>, und Ludwicg,
                                        <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog
                                    <expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, mit <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>glaubbr<ex>ief</ex></expan>, und die von dez
                                        <expan>yczg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dem juden mer jar zu
                                        <expan>erlaube<ex>n</ex></expan> und etlich meyl neher.
                            </note>
</app><app>
<note place="marginleft">
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> in ist zugesagt, der rat meint bey den
                                        <expan>obges<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>jar<ex>en</ex></expan> zu beleiben,
                                    <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ein meyl wegs mag er neher herzu
